Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.holzworth.HS9000, [':ATTACH?', ':CH1:PWR?',
    ':CH1:PWR:MIN?', ':CH1:PWR:MAX?'], [':CH1:CH2:FOO', '0', '-100', '20'],
    sep='\n') as hs:
    channel = hs.channel[0]
    assert channel.power == 0 * dBm
    assert channel.power_min == -100 * dBm
    assert channel.power_max == 20 * dBm
